      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 16:09:55 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Star any transcript line (★) to bookmark a moment</li><li>Copy starred lines as text, each tagged with a `[Frame N · mm:ss]` reference</li><li>Export starred moments as an image — a card per moment with the video still, timecode, and text — straight to the clipboard</li><li>The text tags and the image's "Frame N" labels match, so an LLM can tie each line to its still</li></ul>]]></description>
